\(\angle B\) and \(\angle C\). Give your answer in degrees to at least 3 
decimal places.
$PAR
\{$al->print_q\}    
END_TEXT

$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;
ANS($al->correct_ans);

END_PROBLEM();
